To marry a prince.

38:17.000 --> 38:20.000
His name was Phelan, of the Cantii.

38:20.000 --> 38:22.000
They knew that
if her secret was found out,

38:23.000 --> 38:25.000
it would destroy everything.

38:25.000 --> 38:29.000
Isca, the Devni,
the faith of our tribes.

38:32.000 --> 38:34.000
The princess saw through all the lies.

38:38.000 --> 38:42.000
And one question burned inside her.

38:43.000 --> 38:46.000
"How could the gods allow this?"

38:50.000 --> 38:53.000
The king died.

38:55.000 --> 38:57.000
The queen...

38:58.000 --> 39:00.000
..went slowly mad.

39:03.000 --> 39:04.000
And Andra...

39:07.000 --> 39:09.000
She became the Keeper of the Lake.

39:13.000 --> 39:15.000
And nobody knew the truth.

39:17.000 --> 39:20.000
Nobody except the queen,

39:21.000 --> 39:24.000
the Druid, and the princess.

